org.jetel.graph.extension

Class PortDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.graph.extension.PortDefinition

  • public class PortDefinition
extends java.lang.Object
    Description of input port mapping and record's relations with records from another ports. Also wrapper for read data records.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  PortDefinition.TreeRecord
